{"tid":1421651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好成日叫文宣做野","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:12:00.000Z","uid":182088,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a69618fdf584eeb1d91222772dc27883343a3bd3","tid":1421651,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"整長輩圖其實好易，因為唔需要審美<br />\n連登仔自己搵個photoshop去整學一日就識<br />\n<br />\n剪片就難小小，但好多基本剪接其實都係1-2個鐘就學識，剪一條真相片都唔算難<br />\n但要一個文宣人由0開始自己搵料搵片度flow去做就有d花時間<br />\n你地成日見到政府/黑警講野就咁大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要學識<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>增值自己同極權對抗</strong></span>啊<br />\n<br />\n不論係法律、寫文、學術理論、嘈交、文宣都需要時間去學<br />\n就連危險性最高既前線勇武都要做運動去操fit自己<br />\n希望大家可以認真諗下鐘意邊一個範圍，仔細去鑽研、睇書學習、持之以恆<br />\n將熱血化為動力，成為一個更高Lv既人先可以幫到成件事，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要贏一齊贏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b6b326d5659fea344c5ee127a867ad48b9efd7","tid":1421651,"uid":182088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe6622a8927756738f3b99aa590bfdc7c6e5bcc0","tid":1421651,"uid":46408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n既然無大台<br />\n全部人都係運動既一份子"},{"pid":"0a8c118d14045cd36ffe3045f20dab8a4cc1519a","tid":1421651,"uid":63870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:36:21.000Z","msg":"有時見到咩都開post叫文宣文宣，文宣一百隻手都做唔黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2af28bd447e191418035bd04bb4c1a1f6e527b3","tid":1421651,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"岩  人人都係 文宣 物資"},{"pid":"ad3555cb45527c0988f990ba6fb5f5b25046ddc5","tid":1421651,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"好 文宣做野幫手spread開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edcc1fead559f36e6510c63b1af1ce28698400f","tid":1421651,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"學識整圖整片，搵工都易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563514e26925caef49c0ff4e8bc8b6f637ce9a10","tid":1421651,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"和理非新回合<br />\n［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8ae617a3419b5117511566d7bb2be9615a9ac23","tid":1421651,"uid":182088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:40:02.000Z","msg":"學識剪片仲有個好處<br />\n可以將一套av入面最鐘意果個場景剪出黎<br />\n用幾套av砌一條自己最想睇既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23bcfeb0e6c5e08fdacd26930437def7802d246","tid":1421651,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6bf1f4261e63f5b6c0cd19f92d5640928fbc05a","tid":1421651,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"【教學】自己文宣自己整，自己香港自己救：唔駛Ps/Ai，免費整圖app Canva<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365992</a>"},{"pid":"b8703089fb6c69b571d96da09744dc9b99ed456b","tid":1421651,"uid":24332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"試著不要說警黑勾結 說親政府極端分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1421437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1421437</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"777713054ff37d1878f930c10d1cdb3f366b70f0","tid":1421651,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pi